them out, and rolled her eyes at the end when she tried to cry at the end in a desperate attempt to not walk out carrying the L. REQUEST THE TRANSCRIPTS. Lying your way through the process might work in grandmas family room, but not in the courts where intelligence and facts matter to people who pay attention to things that don't make sense. When I walked out of the courtroom the court clerk said to me, and I quote.."I've never seen anyone come in with the petitioners evidence and none of their own and do what you did, congratulations, give them hell" (Referring to me bringing up the podcast and my molester fams).

They'll take me to court for calling shit out but still haven't held the attempts at incest, child molesters, and their enablers accountable. Disgusting human beings, karma is giving you exactly what you deserve. 

This is chess not checkers, welcome to the first of many L's y'all will take from here on out. But fuck them, I'm glad to be back on my grizz, now it's back to building this empire. üè∞üóΩ

